LOESTRIN 24 Fe is dispensed in a blister card [see HOW SUPPLIED/Storage and Handling]. LOESTRIN 24 FE may be started using either a Day 1 start or a Sunday start (see Table 1). For the first cycle of a Sunday Start regimen, an additional method of contraception must be used until after the first 7 consecutive days of administration.
